data.description: Discover your dream home! A fully renovated 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem in Forest Oaks I, Murfreesboro, at an unbeatable price.The updated kitchen boasts new appliances, granite countertops, new hardware and fresh paint. New door locks, large back patio with covered 2 car parking and storage.  1st floor has large living room, dining room, open den, 1/2 bath and laundry closet. Upstairs has 3 generously sized bedrooms and 2 bath. Primary bath has dual vanities. HOA dues cover pool, clubhouse, fitness center, tennis & basketball courts, playgrounds, exterior & property maintenance.     Easy access to MTSU, shopping, dining, and all Murfreesboro/Nashville and surrounding area entertainment.   Up to $7,500 in Flex Cash available with full price offer, for 3-2-1 Buy-down, points or use towards closing costs. First Year HOA Dues Paid by Seller.   This home will not last long with all the renovations recently completed. Don't miss out on your opportunity to own a great home in a great neighborhood.
